library(magick)
# creat these picture
ghost_image <- image_read(path="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/childrens-responsive-ichef-live/r/720/1x/cbbc/ghosts.jpg")%>%
 image_scale(500)
background_image <- image_read("https://wallpapercave.com/wp/1ecsoou.jpg")



frame1 <-background_image%>%
  image_annotate(text= "HI!",size=200,gravit= "center")%>%
  image_scale(200) %>%
  image_extent("500x500")

frame2 <- background_image %>%
    image_annotate(text= "Hello!",size=200,gravit= "center")%>%
    image_scale(300) %>%
    image_extent("500x500")
  
frame3 <- background_image %>%
    image_annotate(text= "Yo!",size=200,gravit= "center")%>%
    image_scale(400) %>%
    image_extent("500x500")
  
frame4 <- background_image %>%
    image_annotate(text= "Nice to see u~",size=200,gravit= "center")%>%
    image_scale(500)

frame5 <- ghost_image%>%
    image_scale(500)

# creat the animation      
frames <- c(frame1, frame2, frame3, frame4,frame5)

animation <- image_animate(frames, fps = 1)  
image_write(animation, "my_animation.gif")
